---
name: sync-configs
description: Regenerate all AI tool config files from the canonical SOP and tool-specific hints.
user-invocable: true
allowed-tools: Bash, Read, Write, Edit
---

## Steps

1. Run the sync script:
   ```bash
   python tools/sync_configs.py
   ```
2. Verify all outputs were generated:
   - Config files: `CLAUDE.md`, `AGENT.md`, `GEMINI.md`, `.cursorrules`, `.claudecode.md`
   - Symlink: `AGENTS.md` → `AGENT.md`
   - Skills: `.gemini/skills/`, `.cursor/skills/`, `.agents/skills/`
3. Stage and commit the generated files.
